Detailed Description

This section has a list of all the error codes returned when calling Object Detection DPC functions during error conditions.

Base error code for the cfarcaProc DPU is defined in the

#ifndef DP_ERROR_H
#define DP_ERROR_H
/**************************************************************************
* Base Error Code for the mmWave data path DPUs
**************************************************************************/
#define DP_ERRNO_RANGE_PROC_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -100)
#define DP_ERRNO_DOPPLER_PROC_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -200)
#define DP_ERRNO_CFARCA_PROC_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -300)
#define DP_ERRNO_AOA_PROC_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -400)
#define DP_ERRNO_STATIC_CLUTTER_PROC_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -500)
#define DP_ERRNO_DPEDMA_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPU_BASE -600)
/**************************************************************************
* Base Error Code for the mmWave data path DPCs
**************************************************************************/
#define DP_ERRNO_OBJECTDETECTION_BASE (MMWAVE_ERRNO_DPC_BASE -100)
#endif /* DATAPATH_ERROR_H */
